summary: This code appears to be for an ARM64 system, likely running a Linux distribution. It launches Firefox and navigates it to a QR code login endpoint (localhost:8780/v1/Login/GetQRcode). It suggests that removing credential files may be necessary for relogin, possibly supporting multi-logins.
